<p>Next, I start a new <code>R</code> session here, and <code>RStudio</code> will automatically set my directory to this folder. I don‚Äôt need to open the <code>R</code> project to reach this new directory. It will give me access to the folder‚Äôs files, and I can then set a relative path to other files.</p>
